---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Genar - About Me | genar.me" description="Personal website of Genar Trias - Software developer, open source enthusiast">
	<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-mono font-bold mb-6">[genar@localhost ~]$ echo hello world</h1>
		
		<h2 id="About-me" class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">About me</h2>
		
		<p class="mb-4">
			<a href="https://www.gnu.org/philosophy/free-sw.html" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Software Libre</a> supporter, happy 
			<a href="/dev/vim" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">vim</a> user, automatization addict and casual gamer.
		</p>
		
		<p class="mb-4">
			Passionated about Software design, 
			<a href="/dev/continuous-delivery" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">CD</a>, 
			<a href="/dev/continuous-integration" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">CI</a>, 
			<a href="/dev/testing/TDD" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">TDD</a>, 
			<a href="/dev/microservices" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Microservices</a> architecture, 
			<a href="/sys/docker" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">docker</a>, frontend automatization, devops techniques, decentralization and every programming language allowing me to play with all those things.
		</p>
		
		<p class="mb-4">
			I also enjoy <strong>Continuous Learning</strong> and <strong>Continuous Improving</strong>
		</p>
		
		<p class="mb-6">
			I mostly write software using 
			<a href="/dev/javascript" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">javascript</a> 
			(<a href="/dev/javascript/nodejs" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Nodejs</a>, 
			<a href="/dev/javascript/reactjs" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">React.js</a>) and 
			<a href="/dev/php" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">PHP</a> 
			(<a href="/dev/php/Symfony" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Symfony</a>) or 
			<a href="/dev/ruby/rails" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Ruby on Rails</a>.
		</p>
		
		<p class="mb-6">
			I love Sci-FI and cyberpunk.
		</p>
		
		<h2 id="What-things-I-have-done" class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">What things I have done</h2>
		
		<ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-6 space-y-2">
			<li>Check out my projects <a href="/projects" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-mono">&gt; ls src</a></li>
			<li>Check out my jobs <a href="/com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-mono">&gt; ls com</a></li>
			<li>Check out my dev notes <a href="/dev" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-mono">&gt; ls dev</a></li>
		</ul>
		
		<h2 id="What-Technologies-I'm-using-right-now" class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">What Technologies I'm using right now</h2>
		
		<ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-6 space-y-2">
			<li><a href="/dev/ruby/rails" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Ruby on Rails</a></li>
			<li><a href="/dev/javascript/reactjs" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">ReactJS + Redux | Mobx</a></li>
			<li><a href="/dev/javascript/typescript" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">typescript</a></li>
			<li><a href="/dev/javascript/flow" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">flow</a></li>
			<li><a href="/dev/javascript/nodejs" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">nodejs</a></li>
			<li><a href="/dev/javascript/electron" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">electron</a></li>
		</ul>
		
		<h2 id="My-personal-notes" class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">My personal notes</h2>
		
		<ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
			<li><a href="/dev" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">dev</a> &gt; Development notes</li>
			<li><a href="/books" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">books</a> &gt; My book list</li>
			<li><a href="/crypto" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">cryptos</a> &gt; Cryptocurrencies notes</li>
			<li><a href="/gaming" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">gaming</a> &gt; My gaming notes</li>
			<li><a href="/dev/hacking" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">hacking</a> &gt; Hacking & Security</li>
			<li><a href="/sys" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">sys</a> &gt; GNU/Linux and systems notes</li>
			<li><a href="/projects" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">projects</a> &gt; My github projects</li>
			<li><a href="/robotics" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">robotics</a> &gt; Interesting gadgets</li>
		</ul>
